summary: OKAY HI SO, I’m opening commissions for a while in hope to save up some money (#Helpmegetatattoo) and this is what I can offer! ...
caption:
OKAY HI SO,

I’m opening commissions for a while in hope to save up some money (#Helpmegetatattoo) and this is what I can offer! 
Sketch, Lineart, Simple coloring (flat, simple shadow,) and Full color (full shadow/highlight, more life to it all,). I’ve bases the prices on the average time is takes. The price will vary depending on background/ additional characters. I can only accept paypal!   
I will begin with 5 open slots, depending on how this goes. 

I love drawing characters and would love to draw your oc, you, dnd character, favorite character/ ship! (Any fandom but you’ll find my preferred one’s in the tags!)
I’ll keep contact with you during the progress and will send updates and possible changes. It’s important to me for us to keep contact during the progress for the best outcome! 

If you have any questions or if this seems interesting, send me a message and we can talk about it! 

If you can’t commission me but still want to support me you can always reblog! It really helps out! Looking forward to hear from you!  

Kthxbai!
